  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型的工作日流程。标题就叫\"My working day\"吧，分成两个主要阶段：上班路上和实际工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个section分别是\"Go to work\"和\"Work\"。第一个section里您想放哪些具体活动？需要标注参与者和满意度评分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一个section\"Go to work\"里，我早上会先泡茶，这个体验很好，给自己打5分；然后上楼去工作区，稍微麻烦一点，打3分。参与者都是我自己。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加：Make tea: 5: Me 和 Go upstairs: 3: Me。第二个section\"Work\"呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "工作section就一个核心活动：Do work。不过这个体验比较差，只能打1分，毕竟谁喜欢干活呢。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Do work",
        "Work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Do work: 1: Me，放在Work section下。整个journey结构是——标题My working day，两个section，共三个活动节点，评分5、3、1，参与者都是Me。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Work",
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Go upstairs那个，我刚才说的是3分对吧？不是5分，别和泡茶搞混了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go upstairs"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
